OL,5,G2100 The Dark
OL,6,     FWhen a second body is discovered,
OL,7,     FKennedy begins to look for links
OL,8,     Fbetween the victims that could
OL,9,     Fgive her an insight into the
OL,10,     Fkiller's MO. A connection between
OL,11,     Fthe parents of the victims emerges
OL,12,     Fas they are both employed by the
OL,13,     Flocal sawmill and this discovery
OL,14,     Fleads them to look into the
OL,15,     Fowner's son Owen MacLennan, who
OL,16,     Fhas his own chequered past. But is
OL,17,     Fhe the killer they're after? Crime
OL,18,     Fdrama, starring Laura Donnelly
OL,19,G2200 ITV News at Ten; Weather
OL,20,G2230 STV News; Weather
